&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelors, Master’s or PhD degree in chemistry/polymer/engineering, or in general (applied) - science&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least 5 years of relevant work experience&lt;/li&gt;
